{
  "text": "The key examples of groups satisfying the above hypotheses are polycylic groups and wreath products F \u2240 Z with F finite. These groups also have controlled F\u00f8lner pairs in the sense of [CITATION_1] . For these groups we have the following:",
  "correct_citation": {
